  "title": "Circular Economy",
  "description": "A Bitcoin circular economy is a local or digital ecosystem where participants earn, spend, and save bitcoin without converting back to fiat. The goal is to close the loop: merchants accept bitcoin, employees and suppliers are paid in bitcoin, and the community reinvests in bitcoin-native goods and services.",
